RecallNoticeTaskAttachmentForm is a Form
    is primary
    title is "CommentsAndAttachments"
    restrict action MobileCreate
    Layout
        display as text
            paragraph
                RecallNotice
                RecallNotice.Name
                    no label
        single column
            Title
            Comment
        paragraph
            visible when (HasAttachment)
                Attachment.Title
            Attachment.File
                label is "Attachment"
